  "description": "The bounce engine slowed to near-stasis — gravity maximum, damp maximum, count at 8. Each click rebound arrives so far from the attack it feels like a separate event in fog. Sine source is almost invisible. The piece is the silence between the bounces, each one a little farther away, until only the prism reverb remains.",
